                | means any person  or a body corporate willing to donate an Item;
              li
                strong GIVIT Charities
                | means persons of charities, foundations and non government and government organisations such as housing providers, crisis accommodation facilities and emergency relief centres, community mental health agencies, education provides and groups that provide services to underprivileged or people in need;
